						<string>set theText to "You are an expert [ROLE]." &amp; return &amp; "Your goal is to [TASK]." &amp; return &amp; "Audience: [WHO THIS IS FOR]" &amp; return &amp; "Format: [BULLET POINTS / PROSE / TABLE / etc.]" &amp; return &amp; "Length: [BRIEF / STANDARD / DETAILED]" &amp; return &amp; "Constraints:" &amp; return &amp; "- [CONSTRAINT]" &amp; return &amp; "- Do not [THING TO AVOID]" &amp; return &amp; "- Ask clarifying questions if anything is unclear" &amp; return &amp; "" &amp; return &amp; "[PASTE CONTENT HERE]"
